body_html: @daisylab I think your process is correct. i686 by the document would not have SSE, just like if you used 'pentium2'. Nothing extra to add, just wanted to say I think your command-line is correct and there is likely some other reason SSE is added. I do not know enough in this area to debug, just adding moral support. :-)
